335
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,355
Um.

336
00:33:03,876 --> 00:33:05,018
Aren’t you getting up?

337
00:33:06,308 --> 00:33:08,753
You mentioned you have a meeting today about a commercial soundtrack.

338
00:33:11,435 --> 00:33:13,212
