352
00:34:00,993 --> 00:34:02,235
Worry about your work.

353
00:34:03,143 --> 00:34:03,796
Go.

354
00:34:04,204 --> 00:34:05,069
I’ll sleep.

355
00:34:08,952 --> 00:34:09,773
I’m off then.

356
00:34:10,552 --> 00:34:11,731
Call me if you need anything.

357
00:34:42,055 --> 00:34:43,367
Is it influenza?

358
00:34:44,809 --> 00:34:46,288
Just what I thought.

359
00:34:46,841 --> 00:34:48,674
He must have got it from me.

360
00:34:49,126 --> 00:34:51,126
But why does he seem a lot worse than me?

361
00:34:52,471 --> 00:34:55,200
Based on the x-ray result, we discovered a virus in his lungs.

362
00:34:55,396 --> 00:34:57,813
It causes Pneumonia in the patient.

363
00:34:58,297 --> 00:35:02,842
We will first treat him with medications and monitor his condition for complications.

364
00:35:03,192 --> 00:35:06,172
