365
00:35:08,640 --> 00:35:09,762
I’m his boyfriend.

366
00:35:12,891 --> 00:35:15,271
Is there anyone in his family we can contact?

367
00:35:17,988 --> 00:35:19,124
He lives with me.

368
00:35:21,523 --> 00:35:23,013
What about his relatives?

369
00:35:25,866 --> 00:35:26,517
